p:
In the matter of Martin Lawson On Habeaus Corpus In Third Judicial District Washington Territory and now come the plaintiffs by their attorneys and object to the of costs made by Deniah Brown Deputy Clerk on the 16th day of December and object to the item of costs in the fees of D. S. Smith Justice of the peace charging fifteen dollars for holding court five days. That part of the fee bill charging $10 for attorney fee to prevailing concil charging in the fee bill of said D. S. Smith $1.00 commitment.
Ally for plantiff
